RICE is a prioritization framework for product teams. It stands for Reach, Impact, Confidence, and Effort. Features with higher RICE scores should be prioritized first. This framework helps teams make data-driven decisions rather than relying on intuition or the highest-paid-person opinion.

Write script.md (narration script) and outline.md (chapter outline).
Separate them with: ===OUTLINE===

